data.description: This spacious 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home has all the luxuries you are looking for including: freshly paint throughout an open floorplan, luxury laminate flooring, granite countertops, a beautiful tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, a large master suite with your own personal balcony and garden tub, walk-in his and her closets, a bonus room FROG, a 2 car garage and a large fenced in back yard! Located within the Richland 2 school district, this home has access to all the coveted Lake Carolina amenities including various shops, restaurants and entertainment and is also conveniently located minutes from I-77 and I-20. Complete with a one year home warranty, this is a must see!
